export const Projects = [
    {id: "1", name: "ReXplore", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "Exploring how to improve travel planning using insights from locals.", src: "Images-ReXplore/ReXplore.png"},
    {id: "2", name: "eat!", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "A new way to discover and share restaurants.",  src: "Images-eat/eatCover.jpg"},
    {id: "3", name: "JamLink", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "A music streaming service with the connective capability of a social platform.",  src: "Images-jamLink/jamLink.jpg"},
    {id: "4", name: "involveMINT", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "A full redesign of the site for the Pittsburgh non-profit social organization InvolveMINT.", src: "Images-Profile/involveMINT.jpg"},
    {id: "5", name: "Student Feedback Intervention", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "An interface to facilitate feedback among students and teachers during a live presentation.", src: "Images-Profile/TaC.png"},
    {id: "6", name: "Surveillance Capitalism Intervention", category: "UI/UX Design", desc: "An intervention to address unawareness of surveillance capitalism due to systematic unreadability of Terms and Conditions.", src: "Images-Profile/involveMINT.jpg"},
  
    {id: "7", name: "Desktop Organizer", category: "Product Design", desc: "A weekend long sprint to design and prototype a personal desktop organizer.", src: "Images-Profile/desktopOrganizer.jpg"},
    {id: "8", name: "'Steel Hang' Lamp", category: "Product Design", desc: "A lamp design inspired by the appearance, ethos, and history of the city of Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.",  src: "Images-Profile/lamprender.jpg"},
    {id: "9", name: "Silo City Intervention", category: "Product Design", desc: "An architectural exercise in the form of designing an enclosure for a specific animal within an unlikely environment - the old grain silos of Buffalo, NY.",  src: "Images-Profile/silo.png"},
  
    {id: "10", name: "Nat Geo Mock Design", category: "Information Design", desc: "A collection of information in the style of Nat Geo.",  src: "Images-ReXplore/ReXplore.png"},
    {id: "11", name: "Themed Concert Content",  category: "Information Design", desc: "A series of promotional deliverables for a hypothetical music festival.",  src: "Images-ReXplore/ReXplore.png"},
    {id: "12", name: "World Economic Forum Site Design",  category: "Information Design", desc: "World Economic Forum Site Design",  src: "Images-ReXplore/ReXplore.png"},
  
    {id: "13", name: "Computational Art", category: "Digital Media", desc: "Artworks created through programming.", src: "Images-Profile/computational.jpg"},
    {id: "14", name: "Conceptual Precedent Expansion",  category: "Digital Media", desc: "Taking the structural concept and language of a pre-existing building and expanding upon that logic to create a new structure.",  src: "Images-ReXplore/ReXplore.png"},
    {id: "15", name: "Bell Pepper Generative Design",  category: "Digital Media", desc: "Creating a struture by abstracting the generative logic of a bell pepper.",  src: "Images-Profile/pepper.jpg"},
  
  ]
  
  export const Featuring = [
  {id: "1", name: "UI Designer", category: "Experience", company: "Nuance", dates: "05/2022 - Present"},
  {id: "2", name: "Product Management Intern", category: "Experience", company: "Maxar", dates: "05/2021 - 08/2021"},
  {id: "3", name: "UI Design Intern", category: "Experience", company: "involveMINT", dates: "02/2021 - 05/2021"},
  {id: "4", name: "Carnegie Mellon University", category: "Education", dates: "08/2019 - 05/2023"},
  ]
